<body>

  <h1>CSS Keyframe Animation</h1>

  <p>CSS animations allow you to change CSS property values over time. With the proper browser
    prefixing, these animations have pretty good support.
  </p>

  <div class="custom-animation">
      This is a box.
  </div>

<style type="text/css">
@@-webkit-keyframes changify
{
  0% {
    background-color: #000;
    border-radius: 0px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 #000;
    color: #FFF;
    margin-left: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    padding-top: 0;
    width: 50px;
	}
  50% {
    margin-top: 150px;
	}
  100% {
    background-color: #FFF;
    border-radius: 50px;
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 10px #000;
    color: #000;
    margin-left: 250px;
    opacity: 1;
    padding: 50px;
    width: 100px;
	}
}

@@-moz-keyframes changify
{
  0% {
    background-color: #000;
    border-radius: 0px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 #000;
    color: #FFF;
    margin-left: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    padding-top: 0;
    width: 50px;
	}
  50% {
    margin-top: 150px;
	}
  100% {
    background-color: #FFF;
    border-radius: 50px;
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 10px #000;
    color: #000;
    margin-left: 250px;
    opacity: 1;
    padding: 50px;
    width: 100px;
	}
}

@@-ms-keyframes changify
{
  0% {
    background-color: #000;
    border-radius: 0px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 #000;
    color: #FFF;
    margin-left: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    padding-top: 0;
    width: 50px;
	}
  50% {
    margin-top: 150px;
	}
  100% {
    background-color: #FFF;
    border-radius: 50px;
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 10px #000;
    color: #000;
    margin-left: 250px;
    opacity: 1;
    padding: 50px;
    width: 100px;
	}
}

@@keyframes changify
{
  0% {
    background-color: #000;
    border-radius: 0px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 #000;
    color: #FFF;
    margin-left: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    padding-top: 0;
    width: 50px;
	}
  50% {
    margin-top: 150px;
	}
  100% {
    background-color: #FFF;
    border-radius: 50px;
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 10px #000;
    color: #000;
    margin-left: 250px;
    opacity: 1;
    padding: 50px;
    width: 100px;
	}
}
    
.custom-animation {
  border: solid 1px #000;
  padding: 10px;

	-webkit-animation-name: changify;
	-webkit-animation-duration: 1s;
	-webkit-animation-iteration-count: infinite;
	-webkit-animation-direction: alternate;

	-moz-animation-name: changify;
	-moz-animation-duration: 1s;
	-moz-animation-iteration-count: infinite;
	-moz-animation-direction: alternate;

  -ms-animation-name: changify;
	-ms-animation-duration: 1s;
	-ms-animation-iteration-count: infinite;
	-ms-animation-direction: alternate;

  animation-name: changify;
	animation-duration: 1s;
	animation-iteration-count: infinite;
	animation-direction: alternate;
}

  </style>


</body>
</html>
